au.edu.deakin.ice.meltdown

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.edu.deakin.ice.meltdown.GameObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Snowman, Threat

    public class GameObject
extends Object
    A game entity that consists of a bitmap that can be moved and collided with.
